sub_title: Associate Partner at McKinsey & Company | changing organisations for the better
summary: Where people form the core of each company's change engine, I am passionate about anything that makes that engine run faster, smoother, stronger... moving it in the right direction and with great love for each small element. I have extensive experience within organizational and operational transformations, primarily within energy and construction industry, in which I translate vision and strategy to day-to-day reality
